parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The brakes seem to "let loose" when slowing down
making it difficult to stop the vehicle; the vehicle takes longer than expected to come to a complete stop; the brakes do not respond as expected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inequitable braking can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The front brakes do not function properly
causing the vehicle to pull to one side or lose traction; the brakes do not respond as expected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake wear can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The brakes need to be replaced more frequently than expected; the brake pads or rotors wear down quickly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause random and unexplained events, such as interior dome lights coming on, which can be a distraction while driving and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Interior dome lights come on at random
require continuous use of the dome override button to keep the lights off
loss of interior dome lights when doors are open.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system malfunction can cause a fire hazard, which can lead to vehicle damage, injury, or even loss of life.
symptoms: Vehicle catches fire
especially in the windshield area
without warning or indication.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brakes do not work at slow or high speeds
brake pedal goes all the way to the floor
pumping the brakes makes it worse
no warning signs of brake failure (e.g.
squeaking
scraping).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tread separation on Firestone tires can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tread separation
bulging tires
cracks on the sidewall
vibration while driving
loss of tire pressure
tire blowout.
